    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 5-1 guidance for medium-influence, high-consequence, MRL 2 context. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within acceptable error bounds across the full operating envelope. The requirement set (cpb-safety-req-set-v2) enumerates biocompatibility, sterility, electrical safety, and mechanical integrity obligations; other safety properties are enumerated separately. The package is accepted for submission in support of the 510(k) credibility assessment.",
